Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No you won't, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, me and Tabanba play tag! {act he says something like "come to chase me" but idk what it means}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba, watch this! {/this way}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you won't! \NDidn't you hear me? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who turned off the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out to play, Tabanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, you're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? No, it wasn't me... Look, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba! Cock-a-doodle-doo! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, you sick bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I just do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I blamed you, instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... Yeah, you, just... don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you! Just one more chance, Oshiru-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll bring Taruruuto back \Nto the Magic Realm for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Honmaru's mama likes this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oshiru-sensei, the Magic Realm considers you a super-elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If the word gets out that one dropout pupil \Nis leading you a merry dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your peerless career would be tarnished forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd sooner lose my life than fail you, \Nyou can be sure of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please trust me to take care of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to learn how to be quiet now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Ack, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite the superb \Nhome-run on your part, Jabao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it wasn't {\i1}that{\i0} good...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba, here! {TLC, no clue what he might be saying or meaning} {18:40: I'm hearing たばんばおひ\NI know for a fact that he's saying the bird's name here.\NAs for the second part, my best guess is that it's a slightly corrupted version of line 15:20.\NIf that's the case then what you have now is fine. - Aurelius}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Taru, y— {/what're you}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{chirp?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! {gaki?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doncha dare gambol so carelessly, you lousy turkey! {no clue what he means: pretending to be fooling around, finished bird - wondering what's that shiagaru thing, I have an inkling it might be something to do with agaru - to stop, but on this place should be an adjective, like "foolish"} {19:49/18:57: \NFor 18:57, I'm hearing ふざけた真似しやがる鳥だ\NFor 19:49, I'm hearing 誰だこんなことしやがるのは\NBasically, this: https://jisho.org/search/%E3%82%84%E3%81%8C%E3%82%8B - Aurelius}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Takoyaki. Takoyaki! Takoyaki, takoyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba-babanba! Scram! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me noticed first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the smart-ass who put this lousy cage here?! {guess, no clue what he says, shiagaru again? what the fuck, this makes no sense at all now, it's the same word jabao used against him; what the fuck could they possibly mean by finished/completed in both these instances? TLC this and line at 18:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I not make it clear enough \Nthat I want you to stay out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba, it appears that ultimately, \Na third-rate wizard like you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,would never suit me as a right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for you to return to the Magic Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be known that I don't wish to see you \Nmeddling in my affairs ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Oshiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, oh, why? Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, is my snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Honmaru's mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a doctor! \NNo... Only the ambulance would do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But what now? What now? What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? What to do? What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something a human doctor can alleviate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I had reaped the disgust of Teacher Oshiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It all came to Oshiru-sensei disowning me... {/abandoned me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all Taruruuto and Honmaru's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch as I turn upside down  \Nthis sweet little world you've grown used to living in...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if I'm being beckoned... {to tempt; to lure; to entice; to seduce}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With a touch of black magic on this old piece of scrap... {piece of junk; worn-out article}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! It's strictly forbidden in the Magic Realm, \Nbut what does it matter now? {/I don't care}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama, stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ria, is there really no way whatsoever \Nto help cure mom's illness? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, it's not in my power... {/not even sis}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Magic Realm, I've heard about the "Fruit of Life," \Nthat can do anything, including curing this kind of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a million years, \Na single flower blooms, and the fruit is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.18,0:24:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But as for where to look for it... \NAlas, I haven't a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.61,0:24:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine without it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.86,0:24:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't no way you're fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.77,0:24:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.66,0:25:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama won't get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan, you're a big boy now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.16,0:25:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you shouldn't cry, no matter what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.23,0:25:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.18,0:25:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.11,0:26:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me escort you home, Taruruuto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.48,0:26:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you return to the Magic Realm with me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll go look for the Fruit of Life together, \Nto help cure your friend's mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.78,0:26:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish to save your friend's mama, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.21,0:26:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.40,0:26:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But in return, I'll have your promise \Nto not show up in this world ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.69,0:26:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.23,0:27:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alka-gilka, alka-gilka! {no clue if it's random congregation of sounds or derived from something, eg aru ka? giru ka?}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.13,0:27:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Hogeru-ru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.85,0:27:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alka-gilka! Show yourself, Hogeru-ru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.51,0:27:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.33,0:27:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised to Teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.34,0:27:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We return to the Magic Realm together...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.11,0:27:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me love Honmaru's mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.08,0:27:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama mustn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:27:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.08,0:28:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alka-gilka!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.79,0:28:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Hogeru-ru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.84,0:28:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.03,0:28:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Me definitely find the Fruit of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.47,0:28:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.31,0:28:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's mama said that - \Nboys can't cry. Me not cry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.50,0:28:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.45,0:28:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.01,0:28:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.45,0:28:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself! Hogeru-ru-ru-ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.99,0:29:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.92,0:29:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth! Let nothing stop you \Nfrom razing this world to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish bird... {/such stupid thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.80,0:29:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam-bam-crush everything! Bam-boom-pound it! {guess, most likely some another made-up word around banba}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.87,0:29:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.87,0:30:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.25,0:30:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This robot is a piece of scrap, after all. \NIt completely came to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.67,0:30:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The spring finally went unwound, I bet. {deepl has it "The spring has gone haywire." so I agree even though I've no clue what part of it is spring}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if it starts moving again...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.67,0:30:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be a-okay now, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Honmaru! Taru! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.14,0:30:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.68,0:30:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:30:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.65,0:30:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Honmaru? Where were you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen this robot, raging with great power?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.61,0:31:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's certainly but a great piece of scrap now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.07,0:31:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I recalled the effect of Tabanba's magic, \Nthe robot won't return to its original size... {/broke the spell}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.31,0:31:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oshiru-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.69,0:31:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What're y'all so spooked by?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.94,0:32:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{various "Help/save"}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.43,0:33:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic has no effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.57,0:33:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.79,0:33:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oaya-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.49,0:33:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Isn't that Taru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.22,0:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Taru-chan is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.52,0:34:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was naughty of you. \NAren't you a good kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.37,0:34:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.05,0:34:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.65,0:34:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto's got a darn handy pair of toy wings, I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.66,0:34:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub. Rub!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.41,0:34:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good kid, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.56,0:34:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru Taru! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.54,0:34:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! My life saver!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.29,0:35:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This aid isn't meant for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.62,0:35:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The duty of protecting peace in the world is mine to fulfill!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Special Thunder Squadron, \Ncommence the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako Great Special Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.80,0:36:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.66,0:36:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{taru?}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.96,0:37:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you fuss over such trifles!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.80,0:37:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's papa, banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.44,0:37:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got something important to tell you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.29,0:37:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars were moving ominously recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.30,0:37:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I investigated whether or not they foretold a great calamity \Nthat would unleash itself upon our world. And indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.48,0:37:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.51,0:37:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, this world of ours \Nis closely intertwined with the Magic Realm. {lit: constantly threat magic country as well - not sure if they are both threatened, it is threatened by MR, or MR is threatened by it}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.92,0:37:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, both are constantly threatened \Nby hellish powers. {lit: hell country's wicked power is aiming}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.63,0:37:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite possible that this robot \Nis powered by hellish powers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.65,0:37:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been generated \Nfrom the enormous energy of someone's rancor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.91,0:37:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.49,0:38:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that is said \Nto only exist within the Magic Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A fruit amazingly born here, in our very garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.75,0:38:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, this fruit can do anything, \Nincluding curing mom's illness! {had to add a description of its powers as just "fruit of life" kinda only implies it has healing power and I've honestly forgotten myself that its functions are universal}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.38,0:38:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.50,0:38:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fruit of Life appeared once again - \Nsomething that only happens once per million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.89,0:38:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.77,0:38:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When or where it will appear the next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.65,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a mystery to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.69,0:38:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means we'll only ever have one chance to use it, \Nto cure mom's illness! {again, wanna make it clear here they either use it on mom, or on robot as the original narrative is hella cryptic and vague}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.24,0:38:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to decide \Nhow to dispose of this fruit, Honmaru. {/in which way to use it}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.09,0:39:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.72,0:39:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
