Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission is to protect our world's peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody gets away with ruining my city!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.23,0:40:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, what should I do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.46,0:40:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use it now, mom will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.78,0:40:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no one but us is gonna unwind this thing! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.11,0:40:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said, Jabao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.43,0:40:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.70,0:40:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself. {/decide}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.63,0:40:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here, while I avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.31,0:40:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.65,0:41:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, in our world, one lives to help another. {really unsure but hope she means thi}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.79,0:41:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when everyone around is happy, \Ncan you truly be happy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.17,0:41:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.96,0:41:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you should never place your own good \Nabove the good of many. {lit: can't think of your own good only}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.02,0:41:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.87,0:41:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, we'll fix this pile of scrap for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.38,0:41:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.98,0:42:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, I'll buff you up with Inflatable Muscles-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.47,0:42:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.52,0:42:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.86,0:42:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! {guess, maybe banba}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.58,0:42:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Where are my pants going...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.79,0:42:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Banba!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.33,0:42:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanba?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.79,0:43:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He might still be too strong for me, Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.10,0:43:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.19,0:43:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, Power-Upple Juice. Drink this, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, drinking this will make you \Nthousands by thousands stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.04,0:43:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.15,0:43:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The power is overflowing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.09,0:43:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Me go there-re, too! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.48,0:45:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.24,0:45:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Honmaru, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.52,0:45:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! It won't let me get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.50,0:45:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh! Taru's magic wore out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.36,0:45:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.76,0:46:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.93,0:46:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.69,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.42,0:47:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.84,0:47:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have used it to cure mom's illness... \NBut this chance is gone now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.37,0:47:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.88,0:47:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without a fruit only appearing once every million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.59,0:47:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When and where will the next one be born... \Nnot a soul knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.83,0:47:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.10,0:47:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.44,0:47:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun! Taru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.02,0:47:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.01,0:47:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.68,0:47:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We saved everyone else, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.06,0:48:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! The fruit! The light! \NIt showed up!{guess} It's right here!
